text: Toliman or Tolimán may refer to: *The star Alpha Centauri B. *Tolimán (Jalisco), a town in the Mexican state of Jalisco. *Tolimán (Querétaro), a town in the Mexican state of Querétaro. *Volcán Tolimán, a stratovolcano in Guatemala. ==See also== *Tolima (disambiguation) *Tolman
title: Toliman (disambiguation)
